item.title: About
item.description: About Me I am a freshman at Kalamazoo College. As a student who is passionate about Biology and Neuroscience in particular, I aspire to take part in classes, projects, and research labs related to the field. I am also interested in Computer Science with Mathematics and have already self-taught Python for over a year. Education High School for the Gifted, HCMC, Vietnam Aug 2020 - Dec 2023 Honors Class, Biology GPA: 8.6/10
